{"tid":1374422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日雖然臨尾退得唔好 不過其實已經做得好好","createTime":"2019-07-27T18:39:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T19:58:47.000Z","uid":91584,"like":78,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d06c0bb3fc3b66bd97d1ad4b8a10fe3d2e51ff53","tid":1374422,"uid":91584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:39:59.000Z","msg":"班狗今日有好多犯錯 都可以加大文宣力量<br />\n<br />\n1. 9射催淚彈上老人院 上路軌<br />\n<br />\n2. 打社工 向記者用催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n3. 上西鐵站發癲<br />\n<br />\n4. 中聯辦架車<br />\n<br />\n5. 鄉黑拎住枝棍同速龍打氣<br />\n<br />\n呢d都夠大家做文宣 講比市民知班黑警又做柒野<br />\n所以今日我地冇輸到 係臨尾出現左失誤啫<br />\n呢d下次執返好做好d就得 <br />\n我地唔好再覺得咁灰 <br />\n要用今日用血汗換返嚟既野去煲大佢！！！！！！"},{"pid":"3f1cca040d7d5743d2ee92fcff17e4dd7e00b103","tid":1374422,"uid":91584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:43:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d69bdec0d5ed7b37ed18f0bee27c46f1acfef48b","tid":1374422,"uid":99856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:43:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"342c7a85410e249c7747dbd6d9e6bd33ed35e7c5","tid":1374422,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:43:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff994aa765e04fdf7d0d411c8bdd7f00847ae1b","tid":1374422,"uid":283912,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:43:51.000Z","msg":"今日冇入村冇同居民正面衝突已經贏咗<br />\n個道德高地地方依然非常寬敞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b052be4a96c9c99ed0ec2fd3a0a7006666e19bf2","tid":1374422,"uid":91584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dff994aa765e04fdf7d0d411c8bdd7f00847ae1b","tid":1374422,"uid":283912,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:43:51.000Z","msg":"今日冇入村冇同居民正面衝突已經贏咗<br />\n個道德高地地方依然非常寬敞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:45:53.000Z","msg":"冇錯 反而係班狗又搞到見血<br />\n民意冇走到"},{"pid":"316b572a69b1